                                    capacities in your waking hours.
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>
                                <span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
                                    First of all, you need to find out the <b>average length of your sleep cycle</b> -<i> it is likely around 90 minutes</i>. 
