                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">No dawdling. There is always time to relax during the day and before sleeping. You do not need to relax after your alarm clock buzzes.</span></p>
                            <p class="ql-align-center"><br /></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Choose a sleep cycle: [5], [2 + 2], [1 + 1 + 1 + 1].</span></li>
                            </ul>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Set sleep alarms and wake-up alarms.</span></li>
                            </ul>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Get into a routine for sleep preparation and for after waking.</span></li>
                            </ul>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Stick to the routine.</span></li>
