                                    tasks.
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>
                                <span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
                                    You must be fully aware of how each task contributes to the overall goal and why it is important to reach the goal. You have to be driven by a belief that you can actually attain the end outcome and remind yourself of the big
                                    picture as often as you can.
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>
                                <span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
                                    It is also important to remember where you started and all of the tasks you have completed. This is a great way to demonstrate your ability and progress to yourself and generate a self-belief and a feeling of accomplishment.
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p class="ql-align-center"><br /></p>
                            <p class="ql-align-center">
                                <span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">
                                    Think about your long term goal and picture a scene associate with having complete it. Think about the change it will create and all of the results that follow because of it. Think about the subsequent goals you would be focusing on
                                    and the gratitude and appreciation you receive for reaching that point.
                                </span>
                            </p>
                            <p class="ql-align-center"><br /></p>
                            <ul>
                                <li class="ql-align-center"><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Take a prominent image from the last point and imagine it is a printed photograph.<br /><br /></span></li>
                                <li class="ql-align-center"><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Picture the photograph with rubber bands attached to each corner stretching back behind your head.<br /><br /></span></li>
                                <li class="ql-align-center"><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Imagine the photograph is being pulled back away from you as it grows to the size of a cinema screen.<br /><br /></span></li>
                                <li class="ql-align-center"><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Then imagine it is pulled back even further and it is bigger than you can even imagine.<br /><br /></span></li>
                                <li class="ql-align-center"><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">When you feel it is stretch back and out as far as possible, become aware of the massive tension in the rubber bands.<br /><br /></span></li>
                                <li class="ql-align-center"><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">All of a sudden the image is released an it flies back towards you and smashed into your very being.<br /><br /></span></li>
                                <li class="ql-align-center"><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Do this a few times and associate the idea with printing or stamping the outcome onto your subconscious mind.<br /><br /></span></li>
                                <li class="ql-align-center"><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Do this for as many of the preliminary long-term tasks you also need to get done.<br /><br /></span></li>
                                <li class="ql-align-center"><span style="color: black; background-color: rgb(252, 252, 252);">Spend a few minutes remembering all the tasks you have completed already in pursuit it of your end goal.</span></li>
                            </ul>
                            <p class="ql-align-center"><br /></p>
                            <h2 class="ql-align-center"><span style="color: black; background-color: white;">MAINTAINING A PRODUCTIVE MINDSET</span></h2>
                            <p class="ql-align-center"><br /></p>
