                        <h2 style="background-color:darkorange; color:white;">Acetylcholine</h2>
                        <p><br /></p>
                        <p><b>Acetylcholine is synthesized in certain neurons all over the brain.</b> It is a <span style="text-decoration:underline;">neurotransmitter</span> that neurons can use to<i> transmit electrochemical signals</i>.</p>
