                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>It is based on a silently-used sound called a <b>'mantra'.</b></p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p><b>A mantra is a word, phrase, or sound, that you can repeat over and over again</b>. It must be unique; in that, it bears no association in your mind to anything aside from the process of meditation.</p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p><b>You begin by chanting the sound</b> and slowly say it <i>quieter and quieter</i> until it is merely a <b>repetitive thought.</b></p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p><b>Once your mantra is a repeating thought</b>, you let it continue to become <i>quieter and quieter</i> until the mind is in <b>a state of near emptiness</b>.</p>

