                            <h1>HOW LONG SHOULD YOU MEDITATE FOR?</h1>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>As with all of these questions, the answers are dependant on <i>several factors.</i></p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>If you are only just beginning to meditate, or if it's your first time, <b>try not to expect too much from yourself</b>.</p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>Training your mind <i>to <b>focus on a single thing</b>, until all the noise and peripheral thoughts fade away</i>, <b>is a very tricky process</b>.</p>
