            <p><br /></p>
            <p><b style="background-color:yellow;">For perfect healthy skin there is no quick fix solution.</b></p>
            <p><br /></p>
            <p>Try to eat whole-grain plant-based foods, sleep 8 hours a night, go outside everyday and perform at least 30 minutes of cardio.</p>
