                                    <li>Pizza</li>
                                    <li>Bread</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>Some of these seem like unlikely candidates but many products on the market <b>claim to be healthy</b>, and in some ways they are,<span style="background-color:yellow;"><b> but they still contain added sugars</b></span>.</p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>The best way <b>to ensure a reduction of sugar in your diet</b> is to <span style="background-color:yellow;"><b>prepare your own food</b></span> - as far as reasonably practicable, leaving out the sugar <i>(and the salt)</i>.</p>
