                            </div> <p><br /></p>
                            <p><b>Break your day down into three meals</b>; breakfast, lunch, and dinner. Make sure you <b>only eat when you sit down for these meals</b>.</p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>If you elect to have four meals, or five meals, per day, thats okay too - so long as you <b>do so consistently</b> and ensure you are not overeating.</p>
