                            <H2><span class="fa fa-cutlery">  </span>  BREAKFAST</H2>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>This is your chance to build a good healthy habit. Breakfast is the best meal of the day to build into a routine.</p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>Try to use this meal for consuming mostly grains, nuts, and fruits.</p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <img src="~/Content/Images/oatmeal.jpg" />
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <h5>HOW DO I MAKE A WHOLE-GRAIN BREAKFAST?</h5>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>Any type of unsweetened, wholegrain oatmeal, mixed with nuts and fruits will make an ideal breakfast.</p>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <blockquote>Watch out for added sugar! Make sure you buy plain oatmeal, or whole-grain wheat.</blockquote>
                            <p><br /></p>
                            <p>Try not to get fond of a complicated breakfast that takes more than a minute to prepare. Preparation is never a good thing to be relying on when your hungry.</p>

                            <p id="secondfb" style="margin-top:-50px;margin-bottom:100px;"></p>
