                                    <h2>6.&nbsp;MEDITATE</h2>
                                    <p><br /></p>
                                    <blockquote class="quote"><b>Begin the process by meditating</b>. Meditation is an effective method for shutting down the mind and rebooting it in a new state.</blockquote>
                                    <p></p>
                                    <p>For the mind to be <b>suggestible</b>, we must first decide that we are open to suggestions. This means:</p>
                                    <p><br /></p>
                                    <ul>
                                        <li><b>We believe</b> we can soak up our suggestions.</li>
